feedback.overall: I think it looks good! I had the most trouble with the clusters. Maybe add more description into the help section on the extend of the clusters. Because the cluster questions did not have the same highlight interaction as the rest of the questions I am thinking that was on purpose? It left me wanting that functionality though.

feedback.overall: I guess it's my fault for not really knowing what this was testing.  Some of these questions were harder than others and I'm assuming it's down exploring different encoding and searching techniques.  Hope this was helpful! x_x
